label.value: Performed Study Agent Transfer Original Quantity

value.value: The amount and unit of study agent transferred in original units.
The amount and unit of study agent transferred in standard or canonical units.

label.value: Performed Study Subject Milestone Informed Consent Date

value.value: The date (and time) the study subject gives official consent by signing the official consent form.

label.value: Performed Study Subject Milestone Off Study Date

value.value: The date (and time) when the study subject is removed from the study.

label.value: Performed Study Subject Milestone Off Study Reason Code

value.value: A coded value specifying why the subject is removed from a study.

label.value: Performed Study Subject Milestone Registration Date

value.value: The date (and time) the subject has been registered to the study assuming they have finished screening and have been found eligible.

label.value: Performed Study Subject Milestone Study Reference Date Range

value.value: The date and time span used to indicate the start and end of the study for a subject.
The rationale for changing the substance administration in relation to the previous substance administration.

label.value: Performed Substance Administration Change Type Code

value.value: A coded value specifying the modification of the substance administration in relation to the previous substance administration.
The quantity of a substance or medication used in a substance administration.
The textual representation of dosing amounts or a range of dosing information used in a substance administration.

label.value: Performed Substance Administration Dose Frequency Code

value.value: A coded value specifying how often doses are administered.

label.value: Performed Substance Administration Dose Period Code

value.value: A coded value specifying the period during which the periodDoseTotal is administered.

label.value: Performed Substance Administration End Relative To Reference Code

value.value: A coded value specifying when this event ended with respect to the sponsor-defined reference period.

label.value: Performed Substance Administration Period Dose Total

value.value: The total of all doses of treatment in a given period of time (as defined in dosePeriodCode).

label.value: Performed Substance Administration Planned Change Indicator

value.value: Specifies whether a change in the substance administration in relation to the previous substance administration is planned or not.

label.value: Performed Substance Administration Route Of Administration Code

value.value: A coded value specifying the physiological path or method of introducing the substance into or onto the subject.

label.value: Performed Substance Administration Start Relative To Reference Code

value.value: A coded value specifying when this event started with respect to the sponsor-defined reference period.

label.value: Performed Substance Administration Treatment Vehicle Volume

value.value: The quantity and units of treatment vehicle used.
